 <name>Gtk2_PHPConfig</name>
 <channel>pear.php.net</channel>
 <summary>GUI Interface to the php.ini file</summary>
 <description>A user friendly interface to the various configuration
 options available in a php.ini file</description>
 <lead>
  <name>Anant Narayanan</name>
  <user>anant</user>
  <email>anant@php.net</email>
